            <div class="privacy-content">
                <div class="privacy-section">
                    <h2>1. Introduction</h2>
                    <p>LicenseManager ("we", "us", or "our") operates the LicenseManager Discord bot and associated web services (the "Service"). This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your information when you use our Service.</p>
                    
                    <div class="highlight">
                        <p><strong>Important:</strong> By using the Service, you consent to the collection and use of information in accordance with this policy. If you disagree with any part of this policy, please do not use our Service.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="privacy-section">
                    <h2>2. Information We Collect</h2>
                    <p>We collect several types of information from and about users of our Service:</p>
                    
                    <h3>2.1 Discord Information</h3>
                    <p>When you interact with our Discord bot, we may collect:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Discord user ID</li>
                        <li>Username and discriminator</li>
                        <li>Avatar hash</li>
                        <li>Server IDs where the bot is used</li>
                        <li>Role information for license verification</li>
                        <li>Messages sent to the bot in DM or server channels</li>
                    </ul>
                    
                    <h3>2.2 Roblox Information</h3>
                    <p>When you link your Roblox account, we may collect:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Roblox user ID</li>
                        <li>Username</li>
                        <li>Avatar information</li>
                        <li>Game pass/product ownership status</li>
                        <li>Purchase history (for verification purposes)</li>
                    </ul>
                    
                    <h3>2.3 Personal Information</h3>
                    <p>When you register an account, we may collect:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Email address</li>
                        <li>Payment information (processed by third-party processors)</li>
                        <li>IP address and device information</li>
                    </ul>
                    
                    <h3>2.4 Cookies and Tracking Technologies</h3>
                    <p>We use cookies and similar tracking technologies to:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Authenticate users and maintain sessions</li>
                        <li>Remember user preferences</li>
                        <li>Analyze service usage</li>
                        <li>Improve our Service</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                
                <div class="privacy-section">
                    <h2>3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
                    <p>We use the collected information for various purposes:</p>
                    <table>
                        <tr>
                            <th>Purpose</th>
                            <th>Data Used</th>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td>Provide and maintain our Service</td>
